You can choose whether or not to provide personal information through the Next Glass Services. We will not discriminate against you for exercising any of your rights relating to your personal information and will not (i) deny you goods or services,
                  (ii) provide you with a different level or quality of services, or (iii) charge you different prices for services for doing so.
